{"pin":"BH04421","subcodes":[{"code":"BH04421","anchor":"","first_line":"Once again hath the Phoenix of divine grandeur taken flight, and the Raven of glory hath soared from the western horizon of the soul unto the zenith of hallowed eternity [3.5s]... ...Create in me a pure heart, O my God, and renew a tranquil conscience within me, O my Hope!","first_line_orig":"باز بلند مکنت پرواز نمود و غراب غیرت از مغرب جان متصاعد و باوج عماء قدرت... قلباً طاهراً فاخلق فیّ یا الهی سرّاً ساکناً جدّد فیّ یا منائی  ","language":"5","word_count":"210","subjects":"@spiritual transformation, @power and sovereignty of God; omnipotence of God, @prayer for purity; chastity, @detachment; severance; renunciation; patience, @nearness and remoteness, @transcendence; unknowability of God, @composure; tranquillity; serenity","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#494\"\u003eLL#494\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[]},{"code":"BH04421HEA","anchor":"hea","translations":[{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"fo","lang_name":"Faroese"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"gu","lang_name":"Gujarati"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"sm","lang_name":"Samoan"},{"language":"se","lang_name":"Sami"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mt","lang_name":"Maltese"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"},{"language":"sne","lang_name":"Bau Bidayuh"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language"